isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-visits-angolan-port-city-lobito-tout-railway-plans-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯财政部增加延期每日外汇购买</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/russian-finance-ministry-increase-deferred-daily-fx-purchases-2024-12-04/</link><description>俄罗斯财政部周三表示，将在未来六周内增加延期外币和黄金购买量。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:14:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/russian-finance-ministry-increase-deferred-daily-fx-purchases-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示德国企业对中国市场的信心跌至历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/german-firms-china-market-sentiment-falls-record-low-survey-shows-2024-12-04/</link><description>德国商业游说团体周三表示，在华德国企业的商业信心处于历史最低点，因为它们面临着中国日益激烈的竞争和经济放缓。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:05:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/german-firms-china-market-sentiment-falls-record-low-survey-shows-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>经合组织警告全球增长前景面临保护主义风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/oecd-warns-protectionism-risk-global-growth-outlook-2024-12-04/</link><description>经济合作与发展组织周三表示，如果保护主义死灰复燃不会破坏全球贸易复苏，世界经济将在未来两年稳定增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 09:03:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/oecd-warns-protectionism-risk-global-growth-outlook-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车报告 11 月份销量增长 5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-november-sales-up-5-november-2024-12-04/</link><description>沃尔沃汽车周三表示，11 月份销量同比增长 5% 至 66,977 辆，其中欧洲和美国销量领先。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 08:11:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-november-sales-up-5-november-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>尽管美国实施新的出口限制，ASM International 仍重申前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asm-international-maintains-financial-target-despite-new-us-export-restriction-2024-12-04/</link><description>荷兰半导体设备制造商 ASM International 周三表示，根据其初步分析，美国新的出口管制措施与其早些时候的 2025 年前景基本一致。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 07:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asm-international-maintains-financial-target-despite-new-us-export-restriction-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>人民日报称中国可以接受GDP增速低于5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-can-accept-gdp-growth-less-than-5-says-peoples-daily-2024-12-04/</link><description>官方报纸《人民日报》周三表示，中国并不执着于实现特定的GDP增长率，低于5%的经济增速是可以接受的，因为没有必要“崇拜速度”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 07:13:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-can-accept-gdp-growth-less-than-5-says-peoples-daily-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>台北将接待上海代表团罕见的高层访问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taipei-host-shanghai-delegation-rare-high-level-visit-2024-12-04/</link><description>本月晚些时候，台湾首都将接待一个罕见的中国高层代表团，届时上海副市长将访问台湾参加一年一度的城市论坛，此次访问正值台湾海峡两岸紧张局势加剧之际。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 06:45:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taipei-host-shanghai-delegation-rare-high-level-visit-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>小瑙鲁在太平洋影响力之争中与澳大利亚和中国进行会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tiny-nauru-talks-with-australia-china-amid-pacific-influence-tussle-2024-12-04/</link><description>瑙鲁一名官员周三表示，太平洋岛国瑙鲁正在与澳大利亚就移民和经济协议进行谈判，世界第三小国家也在权衡中国的提议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 06:16:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tiny-nauru-talks-with-australia-china-amid-pacific-influence-tussle-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国禁止向美国出口关键矿产后，澳大利亚莱纳斯股价接近三周高点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/australias-lynas-near-3-week-high-after-china-bans-export-critical-minerals-us-2024-12-04/</link><description>在中国禁止向美国出口一些关键矿物的第二天，澳大利亚莱纳斯稀土公司的股价周三攀升至近三周高点。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 06:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/australias-lynas-near-3-week-high-after-china-bans-export-critical-minerals-us-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾和中国就新的南海对抗提出贸易指责</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-ships-entered-its-territorial-waters-around-disputed-shoal-2024-12-04/</link><description>周三，中国和菲律宾对围绕南海有争议浅滩发生的海上对抗给出了相互矛盾的说法，这是这两个邻国之间长期争端的最新争端。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 01:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippine-ships-entered-its-territorial-waters-around-disputed-shoal-2024-12-04/</guid></item><item><title>打击中国电信入侵的美国官员敦促加强加密</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-official-fighting-chinese-telecom-intrusions-urges-more-encryption-2024-12-03/</link><description>一名致力于将涉嫌中国黑客逐出美国电信公司的美国高级官员向他的美国同胞提出了以下建议：</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 19:52:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-official-fighting-chinese-telecom-intrusions-urges-more-encryption-2024-12-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>